      "id": "summary",
      "content": "<p>Self-taught and highly motivated web developer with over 8 years of experience in developing, maintaining, testing, documenting, and troubleshooting web and mobile applications. Strong knowledge in web development principles, including responsive design, separation of concerns, testing, and security hardening. Demonstrated ability to manage projects from start to finish, including client communications and supporting customers. Committed to creating high-quality, readable code and delivering on-time results. Passionate about web application development and quick to learn new technologies.</p>"
